data.description: Come HOME to this 3 Bedroom, 1 bath, ranch with a full basement.  You will love the newly updated kitchen with the perfect garden/greenhouse window. Fresh, neutral paint throughout with a combination of hardwood and luxury vinyl floors. The choice is yours to enjoy the outdoors from the shaded, 3 seasons patio or the sunny deck. Storage space abounds in the 2.5 car detached garage.  All this home needs is YOU!
